OL,3,CParents found guilty of killing their
OL,4,Cbaby boy in Merseyside
OL,6,FA couple have been found guilty of
OL,7,Fmurdering their baby son at Liverpool
OL,8,FCrown Court.
OL,10,FKlevi and Nivalda Santos Pirjani were
OL,11,Ffound to have 'systematically abused'
OL,12,Ftheir son Miguel before his death at
OL,13,Fthe age of 13 weeks in November last
OL,14,Fyear.
OL,16,FThe baby boy was found with numerous
OL,17,Fbroken bones and a bleed on the brain.
OL,18,FThe pair tried to blame each other for
OL,19,Ftheir son's death, but they were
OL,20,Funanimously convicted of Miguel's
OL,21,Fmurder on 29 October.
