OL,3,CParents found guilty of killing their
OL,4,Cbaby boy in Merseyside
OL,6,FThe couple were both was in tears in
OL,7,Fthe dock as the verdict was returned,
OL,8,Fas were the jury of six men and six
OL,9,Fwomen.
OL,11,FNivalda Pirjani had previously
OL,12,Fadmitted the lesser charge of allowing
OL,13,For causing the death of a child.
OL,15,FThey will be sentenced at a later
OL,16,Fdate, with Mr Justice Baker, who
OL,17,Fpresided over the trial, further
OL,18,Fremanding them into custody.
