OL,3,CParents found guilty of killing their
OL,4,Cbaby boy in Merseyside
OL,6,FKlevi Pirjani called 999 shortly
OL,7,Fbefore midday on November 24 2024 to
OL,8,Freport that Miguel was unresponsive.
OL,9,FPeter Wright KC, prosecuting, told the
OL,10,Fcourt: "He told the operator that
OL,11,FMiguel just stopped breathing.
OL,13,F"Curiously, he referred to his son as
OL,14,Fit. It just stopped breathing. It is a
OL,15,Fmatter for you to consider in due
OL,16,Fcourse as to whether this was a
OL,17,Fproduct of distress on his part, a
OL,18,Flanguage barrier or an unintended
OL,19,Findication of his attitude towards
OL,20,FMiguel."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/21
