OL,6,FEmergency services attended the family
OL,7,Fhome on Percy Road in Seacombe,
OL,8,FWirral, "within minutes" and found the
OL,9,Fbaby in cardiac arrest. While
OL,10,Fparamedics were able to recover a
OL,11,Fpulse, he was subsequently taken to
OL,12,FAlder Hey Children's Hospital in an
OL,13,F"extremely serious" condition.
