OL,4,Cbaby boy in Merseyside
OL,6,FMiguel remained in an unconscious
OL,7,Fstate over the coming days, although
OL,8,Fhis injuries were ultimately found to
OL,9,Fbe "irreversible". He remained on life
OL,10,Fsupport until November 29 2024, when
OL,11,Fhe died following the removal of
OL,12,Fartificial ventilation.
OL,14,FMr Wright continued during his
OL,15,Fopening: "At the time of his passing,
OL,16,Fhis mother was permitted to hold his
OL,17,Fhand. Whilst present, she was heard to
OL,18,Fsay 'I should have protected you'."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/21
