OL,6,FA post mortem examination later
OL,7,Frevealed further injuries, including
OL,8,Fretinal haemorrhages, displaced skull
OL,9,Fbones, bleeding on both sides of the
OL,10,Fbrain, bleeding around the cervical
OL,11,Fcord and a fatal hypoxic ischaemic
OL,12,Fbrain injury. Under interview, Nivalda
OL,13,FPirjani gave a prepared statement to
OL,14,Fdetectives in which she described
OL,15,FKlevi as being abusive and violent.
