OL,6,FThe 34-year-old added that she did not
OL,7,Fblame her partner for Miguel's
OL,8,Finjuries but said "she was frightened
OL,9,Fof him and feared what he may do". She
OL,10,Falso went on to repeat her claim that
OL,11,Fher husband was the one responsible
OL,12,Ffor looking after Miguel.
