OL,6,FBut Mr Wright said of this account:
OL,7,F"We say her account is a fiction,
OL,8,Fcalculated to conceal her own
OL,9,Finvolvement in these events and to
OL,10,Finfer that any responsibility for the
OL,11,Finjuries sustained by Miguel and his
OL,12,Fdeath are the sole responsibility of
OL,13,Fher partner Klevi. We say they were in
OL,14,Fit together from the start."
