OL,6,FIn her evidence, Nivalda Pirjani told
OL,7,Fthe court that she met her husband and
OL,8,Fco-defendant online in 2014, when she
OL,9,Fwas living in Kirkby and he was
OL,10,Fresiding in Birmingham, before they
OL,11,Fmoved in together in 2016. But she
OL,12,Fsaid: "I've always been scared of
OL,13,FKlevi. I was scared of Klevi trying to
OL,14,Fdo something to me, because Klevi can
OL,15,Fbe violent, aggressive, lose control.
OL,16,FHe would give a slap and beat me, on
OL,17,Fthe face and on my body."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/21
