OL,6,FAsked whether she had previously tried
OL,7,Fto leave the relationship, Pirjani
OL,8,Fsaid: "Klevi stopped me all the time.
OL,9,FShouting, frightening, scaring me. I
OL,10,Fjust tried to run away from the house.
OL,11,FHe tried to be aggressive with me,
OL,12,Flost control, shouting and tried to
OL,13,Fbeat me as well."
OL,15,FMiguel was then born on August 27 2024
OL,16,Fand spent the first six weeks of his
OL,17,Flife in hospital due to medical issues.
