OL,6,FKlevi Pirjani meanwhile told the jury
OL,7,Fof they had had a "good relationship,
OL,8,Fvery strong" and denied being violent
OL,9,For controlling towards his wife. The
OL,10,Fformer chef and digger driver went on
OL,11,Fto describe himself as "the best dad
OL,12,Fin the world", saying of the moment
OL,13,Fthat he learned he was going to have a
OL,14,Fson: "It was a dream for me. My
OL,15,FMiguel."
OL,17,FKlevi Pirjani said "How can I harm my
OL,18,Fson? Never can I harm my son."
