OL,6,FThe defence silk subsequently put to
OL,7,Fhim: "Mr Pirjani, the injuries to your
OL,8,Fbaby son were extensive, devastating
OL,9,Fand fatal. Did you cause any of those
OL,10,Finjuries?"
OL,12,FPirjani then appeared to become
OL,13,Femotional as he responded: "How can I
OL,14,Fharm my son? I never would do that. I
OL,15,Flove my son so much. My blood, you
OL,16,Fknow. I cared for him, the best
OL,17,Ftreatment for him. I loved him so
OL,18,Fmuch."
