OL,6,FAsked who had caused the injuries that
OL,7,Fled to Miguel's death, Pirjani said "I
OL,8,Fdon't know". He also said he had not
OL,9,F"seen them being caused", before Mr
OL,10,FBowers put to him: "If it wasn't you,
OL,11,FMr Pirjani, then who was it?"
OL,13,FPirjani replied "Nivalda" before
OL,14,Fadding "I didn't see". Mr Bowers
OL,15,Fcontinued: "You can't quite bring
OL,16,Fyourself to tell that last lie, can
OL,17,Fyou? You did not see, so you say,
OL,18,FNivalda commit any assault on Miguel.
OL,19,FAnd yet you are blaming her, aren't
OL,20,Fyou?"
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G17/21
