OL,6,FBut Pirjani said "no, I'm not blaming
OL,7,Fher". When Mr Bowers asked "who are
OL,8,Fyou blaming then, who did it?", he
OL,9,Fresponded: "I don't know. I haven't
OL,10,Fseen. I never seen those injuries.
OL,11,FWhat can I say, if I never seen those
OL,12,Finjuries? I didn't do it."
