OL,6,FMr Bowers went on to reference a text
OL,7,Fmessage, sent from Klevi Pirjani to
OL,8,FNivalda Pirjani prior to Miguel's
OL,9,Fdeath, in which he said "I'm feeding
OL,10,Fyour bishe". While the defendant
OL,11,Fmaintained that the final word meant
OL,12,F"hero" in Albanian, it was put to him:
OL,13,F"It means monster. It means beast. I'm
OL,14,Ffeeding your beast."
