OL,6,FPirjani however said "no, that's not
OL,7,Ftrue". Mr Bowers then alleged that he
OL,8,F"didn't like the fact that Miguel was
OL,9,Fborn with abnormalities and
OL,10,Fdifficulties" to which he replied:
OL,11,F"How can you say I didn't like Miguel
OL,12,Fif I never missed an appointment? How
OL,13,Fdidn't I care for my son?"
OL,15,FMr Bowers then said: "You cared so
OL,16,Fwell for your son that you have no
OL,17,Fidea how he came by 41 fractures and
OL,18,Fsuffered a fatal blow to the head. Is
OL,19,Fthat right?"
